4pt">Network Rail invests in a wide-ranging </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">programme</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">, working with national and local </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">organisations</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">, to ensure that level crossings are safe and helping people use them correctly.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:112%; margin:10.8pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">There have been a number of high profile and tragic incidents at level crossings over the years, suggesting more needs to be done to educate drivers about the risks at level crossings. Combining education with 'enforcement' will ensure compliance is maintained.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:112%; margin:10.8pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">StarTraq</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"> traffic enforcement systems are designed to help the Police discourage individuals from breaking the rules.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:112%; margin:10.8pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">Some traffic offences are criminal and so enforced by the Police, others are civil offences and enforced by local authorities.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:112%; margin:10.8pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">Enforcement activity is also carried out by private contractors, for example controlling parking on private land.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:112%; margin:10.8pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">StarTraq's</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"> history and core expertise stems from working with the Police and enforcement agencies to process traffic offences. Our systems are both secure and flexible.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:112%; margin:10.8pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">StarTraq's</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"> modular system can provide Network Rail and BTP with an integrated solution, which can provide adjudication, document management and automated workflow allowing offenders to be processed according to the severity of the offence, offering educational alternatives to 'Fixed Penalty'.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:84%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:84%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:84%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Introduction:</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:120%; margin:12.6pt 0pt 0pt 39.6pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10pt; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">1.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="603" height="37" alt="" style="float:left; margin:0pt" /><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">StarTraq</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.1pt"> seeks to drive safety enhancements for all road users through </span><span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">education </span><span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">and enforcement. </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">StarTraq</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> software solutions are designed for processing different </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.25pt">types of offences and for delivering </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; f