; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10pt; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">9.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt"> Having all offences handled via one single platform provides the additional benefit of efficient and accurate reporting.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:83%; margin:12.6pt 0pt 0pt 25.2pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:83%; margin:12.6pt 0pt 0pt 25.2pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Evidence for consideration:</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:16.2pt 10.8pt 0pt 28.8pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt">10.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt">A </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt">StarTraq</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> system has the ability to automatically read a vehicle registration mark and offence details using optical character recognition (OCR) and automatic number plate </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.45pt">recognition (ANPR) on both analogue and digital offences. Alternatively, if ANPR data </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.55pt">is provided by the camera technology then this can be uploaded to a </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.55pt">StarTraq</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> system </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">and displayed alongside the offence image.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:117%; margin:12.6pt 10.8pt 0pt 28.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt">11.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.55pt">The System can be deployed securely on the Cloud, so it is ideal for remote locations </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.3pt">such as level crossings.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:14.4pt 10.8pt 0pt 28.8pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt">12.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.35pt">With a direct connection to the Police National Computer (PNC) a </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.35pt">StarTraq</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.35pt"> system </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.55pt">can check the vehicle and keeper identity reporting back to the verifier the keeper's </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.35pt">address details and the current status of the vehicle (for example, if it has been </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.6pt">reported stolen).</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:14.4pt 10.8pt 0pt 28.8pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt">13.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.75pt">The </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.75pt">StarTraq</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.75pt"> system can display multiple images and video clips to the verifier. Image </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.35pt">enhancement tools allow the verifier to accurately record offences. Rejection codes </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.5pt">for exempt vehicles (such as police, ambulance and fire engines) can be used so that </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">an outcome for every offence is achieved.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:14.4pt 10.8pt 0pt 28.8pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt">14.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.5pt">The output from </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.5pt">StarTraq</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.5pt"> system is a comprehensive file of driver names, addresses </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.45pt">and date of birth along with offence details ready for processing. This output file can </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.6pt">also be </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.6pt">customised</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.6pt"> ready to export to a 3rd party system, such as education course </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.2pt">provider.</span></p><p style="margin:14.4pt 0pt 0pt 28.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt">15.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.15pt">Tools for adding officer issued tickets to the database are also available.</span></p><p style="margin:16.2pt 0pt 0pt 28.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt">16.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.05pt">A </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.05pt">StarTraq</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.05pt"> system will help Network Rail to:</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:18pt 10.8pt 0pt 64.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.45pt">Process offences without the need for adding to headcount thereby keeping costs down and guaranteeing a return on investment.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:118%; margin:14.4pt 10.8pt 0pt 64.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.45pt">Centralise</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.45pt"> processing of offences maintaining the flexibility to allow for multi-</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">site operations.</span></p><p style="margin:14.4pt 0pt 0pt 64.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.15pt">Operate a system that is flexible, user friendly and dynamic.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:18pt 10.8pt 0pt 64.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.25pt">Customise</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.25pt"> the workflow to map a process bespoke to Network Rail/BTP </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.45pt">automating much of the offence lifecycle.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:114%; margin:14.4pt 7.2pt 0pt 64.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.15pt">Give confidence that a </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.15pt">StarTraq</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.15pt"> system is camera vendor independent </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">software supporting interfaces from all camera types.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:114%; margin:14.4pt 7.2pt 0pt 64.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.25pt">Provide a seamless diversion of offenders to court or driver education —</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">determined by Network Rail.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:114%; margin:14.4pt 7.2pt 0pt 64.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.1pt">Provide court files at the click of a button.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:114%; margin:14.4pt 7.2pt 0pt 64.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt">Future proof</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> a system protecting against any legislation and camera hardware </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt">changes.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:114%; margin:14.4pt 7.2pt 0pt 64.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt">Reduce on-going IT support costs.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:114%; margin:14.4pt 7.2pt 0pt 64.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.55pt">Send correspondence in multiple languages to offenders and/or refer offenders </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.5pt">to a website for trusted translation.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:114%; margin:14.4pt 7.2pt 0pt 64.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.65pt">View offence images online and any other details that Network Rail/BTP deem </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.5pt">appropriate.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:114%; margin:14.4pt 7.2pt 0pt 64.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.6pt">Fully integrate with handheld devices or scan paper tickets supporting process </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">officer manually generated issued tickets.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:114%; margin:14.4pt 7.2pt 0pt 64.8pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.6pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt">Offer e-learning as part of an overall driver education strategy. </span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:227%; margin:16.2pt 79.2pt 0pt 0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Recommendation:</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:114%; margin:12.6pt 0pt 0pt 39.6pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.75pt">17.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.75pt">StarTraq's</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.75pt"> recommended solution to support level crossing safety improvements is for </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.55pt">Network Rail and its enforcement partner (BTP) to </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.55pt">adopt an enforcement protocol that </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.75pt">is fair, transparent, trusted and reliable. A </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.75pt">StarTraq</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.75pt"> system will provide a sophisticated workflow and document management capability Network Rail to process level crossing </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.35pt">offences from different camera types through to a successful outcome e.g. fine, </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.5pt">education or court.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:114%; margin:12.6pt 0pt 0pt 39.6pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.75pt">18.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt">StarTraq</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.7pt"> recommends that Government looks to introduce an enforcement solution for </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.45pt">level crossing safety, drawing on the results and benefits that have been gained by </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">other enforcement agencies. By taking a targeted approach to casualty reduction </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.75pt">where education and enforcement work together, compliance at level crossings will be </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt">achieved.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:114%; margin:12.6pt 0pt 0pt 39.6pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10.5pt; letter-spacing:-0.75pt">19.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.55pt">Lastly </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.55pt">StarTraq</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.55pt"> recommends that the Office of Rail Regulator (ORR) works with the </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.45pt">Parliamentary Advisory Council for Transport Safety and Royal Society for Prevention </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.3pt">of Accidents (</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.3pt">RoSPA</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.3pt">) to devise a comprehensive package of educational courses </span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">aimed at Level Crossing offenders so that road users are offered a real alternative to a fixed penalty once an offence has been committed.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:114%; margin:12.6pt 0pt 0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; letter-spacing:-0.4pt">July</span><span style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; letter-spacing:-0.4pt"> 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>